title: Doctor Who Unleashed S01 William Hartnell 1963 [B+W]
description:
Doctor Who Unleashed Season 01 extended 1963 story in Black & White (William Hartnell)
                 Video = 720x400 [Widescreen]     &     Audio = Stereo 
See the original 1963 Doctor Who (Mr William Hartnell R.I.P)  Like you've never seen before, this extended and updated collection has been several years in the making (I have been collecting footage for this since 2012), this is nothing like any version ever seen before . 
Guest appearances from John Hurt, David Tennant, Matt Smith, Paul McGann, Christopher Eccleston, Peter Capaldi, Jenna Louise Coleman, Peter Cushing, Roberta Torvey, Tom Baker, and a whole range of stars you never imagined. 
This is the origins of Doctor Who, and of the greatest enemies the universe has ever seen, there are just over 4 seasons of William Hartnell, and this is just the beginning. See his story restored as much as possible, but the surprises this Unleashed series will bestow on you will tantalize all Whovians, even the War Doctors story crosses paths with the recent Doctor (Capaldi), showing where the War Doctor went after his 3 Doctor experience in the Day Of The Doctor.
